snippet.title: DND gameplay (PC Game, 1984)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for DND, Dos PC game produced by R O Software in 1984 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/dnd/3987/
The whole game is played in timed delay, it is turn-based. During the game, you will encounter monsters which you can fight to gain experience points.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Ultima 8 - https://youtu.be/Ry3lCdwJ3yU
Dungeon Quest - https://youtu.be/Jt-USfOIvLs
